snippet.title: Pucca n' Friend (Gameplay iOS / Android)
snippet.description:
Pucca n' Friend (Gameplay iOS / Android)

Download : http://appgamed.com/review_app.php?id=1525&game=Pucca-n-Friend

The fate of a restaurant rests squarely in your hand. Begin as an unknown chef and work your way up to a world class culinary master status.
Design an aesthetic but yet functional restaurant, serve up 70 different recipes, and check out how your friends or neighbors are decorating through the world’s restaurant guidebook.
